700866f-b.text:
(1)
Dewey Ave., at Throgas Neck Boulevard (vantage point). The view is eastward across Weir Creek and shows the Edgewater Park bungalow colony on the shore of Long Island Sound.
July 1, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
A closer view of the same showing the Creek (right) and Sound
more prominently.
July 1, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
700866f-b.original_title: Bronx: Dewey Avenue - Throggs Neck Boulevard
